"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1167647","Ministry of Defence","false","2019-11-05","<p>I refer the hon. Member to the answer I gave on 4 November 2019 to the hon. Members for Moray (Douglas Ross), Harrow East (Bob Blackman), Havant (Alan Mak), Angus (Kirsten Hair), Chatham and Aylesford (Tracey Crouch), Clacton (Giles Watling), West Worcestershire (Harriett Baldwin), North East Hampshire (Ranil Jayawardena) and Cheadle (Mary Robinson) to Questions 7761, 7715, 7772, 7783, 7723, 7790, 7738, 7794 and 7796.</p>","Berwick-upon-Tweed","Anne-Marie Trevelyan",,"2019-11-05T11:54:08.6Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1167647/answer","Biography information for Anne-Marie Trevelyan","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1167647/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1167647/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2019-10-31","Ministry of Defence: Public Expenditure","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, what assessment his Department has made of the effect on the (a) prosperity and (b) economy of local areas in which armed forces are based of spending by (i) his Department and (ii) those armed forces in each year since 2010; and if he will place that information in the Library.","false","Biography information for Kevin Hollinrake","Thirsk and Malton","Kevin Hollinrake","8266"
